    <p><strong>We don't do:</strong> new prep table installation (specialty installer trade); cutting board replacement (carpenter or fabricator); new sneeze guard fabrication (sheet metal trade, though we adjust existing sneeze guards as part of refrigeration diagnosis); food prep equipment beyond refrigerated tables (slicers, mixers, see <a href="/commercial/">commercial appliance repair</a> for that catalog).</p>

    <p>If you're not sure whether your unit falls under our scope, call. We tell you on the phone, before the dispatch fee, whether the work is ours or whether you need a different trade.</p>
